      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and<strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
