      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>dried oregano </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic & herb dip</strong></p>",
