    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash and tear your<strong> lettuce</strong> into rough pieces</p><p>Once the corn is tender, stand them upright and slice the <strong>corn</strong> from the cobs using a sharp knife (be very careful!), then discard the cobs</p><p>Add the<strong> torn lettuce </strong>and<strong> sliced corn</strong> to a large bowl and toss it all together – this is your <strong>corn salad</strong></p>",
