      "instruction": "<p>Tear your <strong>basil leaves</strong> over the <strong>cheesy pepperoni pizza loaded fries </strong>and serve the <strong>corn salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>garlic & herb dip</strong> over the salad and use the rest for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
